sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeGW as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS
    participant API as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP<br/>(in-pod, localhost)
    participant Worker as HPUWorker<br/>(in-process)
    participant Gaudi as Intel Gaudi Device<br/>SynapseAI HAL

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 1: Model Inference Request

    Client->>KServeGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    KServeGW->>RBAC: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    RBAC->>API: Forward (HTTP/8000)<br/>localhost, no auth
    API->>Worker: In-process call<br/>Schedule inference
    Worker->>Gaudi: SynapseAI HAL<br/>Graph execution
    Gaudi-->>Worker: Inference result
    Worker-->>API: Generated tokens
    API-->>RBAC: JSON Response
    RBAC-->>KServeGW: HTTPS Response
    KServeGW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 2: Multi-Card Tensor Parallelism

    participant Worker0 as HPUWorker Rank 0
    participant WorkerN as HPUWorker Rank N

    Worker0->>WorkerN: HCCL all-reduce<br/>Dynamic port<br/>Plaintext (in-cluster)
    WorkerN-->>Worker0: Collective result

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup

    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    API->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Access Key
    S3-->>API: Model artifacts
    API->>HF: Download tokenizer/config<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    HF-->>API: Model config files

    Note over Client,Gaudi: Flow 4: KV Cache Disaggregation (NIXL)

    participant Prefill as Prefill Instance
    participant NIXL as NIXL Side Channel<br/>HTTP, Plaintext
    participant Decode as Decode Instance

    Prefill->>NIXL: KV transfer coordination<br/>VLLM_NIXL_SIDE_CHANNEL_PORT + dp_rank
    Prefill->>Decode: KV cache transfer<br/>NIXL / RDMA<br/>Plaintext, No auth
